AGI -&nbsp;&nbsp;"It is a mistake to make the electoral campaign prevail over the hypothesis of division of the center-right, it is the only favor that can really be done on the left." It is a new call not to feed internal clashes to the coalition that relaunches Prime Minister Meloni who today was in Campobasso and in Potenza to sign the cohesion pacts that guarantee funds to Molise and Basilicata. In the alliance of government there are three forces that reside in different families > and the debate is on how to place themselves in view of Europeans. After the event organized by Identity and Democracy in Rome, during which the Secretary of the League of Salvini reiterated its support to von der Leyen and criticism of France for the attitude on the war between Ukraine and Russia, the President of the Council threw water on fire. "We're all in election campaigns and campaigns I understand. Then I'm not worried. Everyone knows in Italy and abroad that if there is one who has never ruled and will never rule with the left is called Giorgia Meloni", he cut short. The premier had been released directly from Marine Le Pen.
&nbsp;
"Everyone knows what is the strategy I have in Europe and I do for granted that it is shared by all the forces of majority, that of bringing a majority of centerright also in Europe," pointed out the head of the executive who confirmed the will to dissolve the reserve on its descent into the field at the June appointment only at the last useful moment.
&nbsp;
"I said I'll decide at the end," he said. But its main objective is to make sure that in a challenge that will be played with proportional the centerpiece does not make autogol. Support for von der Leyen >o no? "The theme is not the chairman of the committee, the theme is the majority supporting the chairman of the committee because&nbsp; it is that majority deciding the policies that are made in Europe," said Meloni.&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;
In close circle the League has expressed that - it has evidenced as for months "auspica unito center, in Europe as in Italy".
"Unfortunately, until today - it has emphasized - "the only vetoes on the Le Pen and the allies of the League have arrived. We hope that no one, in the coalition leading the country, prefers to rule the EU with Macron and the socialists, rather than with the League and its allies." Also the secretary of FI Tajani has returned on the initiative promoted Saturday in the Capital with Salvini and the European sovereign parties, claiming that the alliance of centerright is solid and that the government goes on.
&nbsp;
"This - it has observed - is not a sovereign government, it is a center-right government that has within it Forza Italia, strong presence in the European popular party. A strong Europeanist force." And again: "It's not about Le Pen or Le Pen. We are neither with Le Pen nor with Afd. We are Europeanists, we are for NATO and we follow our line".<br> On the theme of alliances in Europe the vice-premier and foreign minister said he did not want to make controversy: "It's not useful. Central-right voters don't want any controversy. We are the Ppe and there is no government agreement that obliges us to be part of the same family. I'm convinced that the Ppe will win the election. The Treaty stipulates that the chairman of the committee goes to the party which wins the elections. If there is someone who has driven Europe the alternative to the left was I in 2017." The words of Salvini on Macron? "It's not my language."
<br> "I understand that Salvini wants to cover the same electoral space as Europeans in 2019, but they were held in a very different historical phase. It's legitimate. But it must never be forgotten that the other plan on which we must move is the internal one, of the government", said the leader of Noi Moderati, Lupi, in an interview with the Corriere della Sera.&nbsp;

